item.title: 【Unreleased/Unofficial (lossless)】FLAC - S Club 7 - S Club Party Live (2001)
item.description:
​

S Club Party Live 2001 was the first concert tour of British pop group S Club 7. Footage taken from the Manchester Evening News Arena performance was released as a DVD, S Club Party Live, that same year.

Audio ripped directly from the official concert DVD.​

1. The Party Begins (Intro)
2. Don't Stop Movin'
3. You're My Number One
4. Friday Night
5. Our Time Has Come
6. Stand by You
7. Two In A Million
8. I Really Miss You
9. She's Out of My Life (Jon Lee solo)
10. You
11. Natural
12. Bring It All Back
13. Viva La Fiesta
14. Never Had A Dream Come True
15. Bring the House Down
16. Love Train
17. Reach
18. S Club Party
